{"nodes":[{"id":"1aeacca8-df99-4d1e-b22a-253661dcc4fb","chapterId":"caf88652-0509-4d8e-b6e5-9f526cc7bd97","title":"Утро","content":{"items":[{"id":"85b09749-b8bd-4be3-be2b-eed7ea62c72d","type":"text","text":"Сегодня я проснулся позже обычного и проспал школу.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"041ac311-ddf9-4346-aec3-17d47ceaf729","type":"button","text":"Пойти в школу","targetNodeId":"faf1f565-11dd-447a-a2b6-d9473727ca8f","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":0.0,"y":0.0,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0,"backgroundAssetId":"71aa4a0b-9b3e-4adb-b26a-35cf5373a750.jpg","color":4280492835},{"id":"faf1f565-11dd-447a-a2b6-d9473727ca8f","chapterId":"caf88652-0509-4d8e-b6e5-9f526cc7bd97","title":"Пойти в школу","content":{"items":[{"id":"9ec8c342-7e36-415b-8eeb-d238b6197319","type":"text","text":"Асфальт под ногами пошёл трещинами — значит, скоро поворот во дворы. Воздух пахнет бензином от проезжающей маршрутки и почему-то свежим хлебом из будки, которая откроется только через час. Прохожу мимо ларька с мороженым, он пока на замке, и сворачиваю в арку.\n\nВо дворах всегда тише. Бабка с тележкой копается в скамейке, ей помогать не надо, она сама справляется. Мужик в синей спецовке грузит какие-то мешки в багажник. Я срезаю путь через детскую площадку, качели скрипят на ветру, хотя на них никого нет.\n\nЯ на месте.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"ae3a98e6-8267-46df-8a8a-2439ff54d240","type":"button","text":"Зайти в школу","targetNodeId":"31b052bd-1b6b-49a1-b026-5220362c536b","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":0.0,"y":200.0,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0,"backgroundAssetId":"11d60557-c8c1-4916-9a19-83b70fe03abd.jpg","color":4280492835},{"id":"31b052bd-1b6b-49a1-b026-5220362c536b","chapterId":"caf88652-0509-4d8e-b6e5-9f526cc7bd97","title":"Зайти в школу","content":{"items":[{"id":"0dff6d68-5d1b-4303-800d-795e9da0b99d","type":"text","text":"Я зашёл в школу.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"252ebfa6-ce9f-47e5-826c-c7a3cd4c013e","type":"text","text":"В холле пусто и звенит тишина, только где-то далеко гудят лампы дневного света. Времени нет — опаздываю.\nБыстро переобуваюсь и бегу к гардеробу. Дёргаю ручку — заперто. Чёрт! Обычно в таких случаях кто-нибудь просит вахтёршу или уборщицу открыть, но я даже имён их не знаю.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"6c087183-63b9-413d-8bb3-d8543c6a2ff2","type":"button","text":"Засунуть сменку в рюкзак","targetNodeId":"43060fae-d73c-4a6b-92a3-6bd93ce48c96","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"90697fbe-23ea-4dca-aa2e-494c13d44399","type":"button","text":"Дождаться звонка здесь","targetNodeId":"6ddca9f8-283a-4d24-a159-d0b043bd5c22","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":0.0,"y":400.0,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0,"backgroundAssetId":"3585a2f8-8c59-4a10-92da-e92f3daced77.jpg","color":4280492835},{"id":"43060fae-d73c-4a6b-92a3-6bd93ce48c96","chapterId":"caf88652-0509-4d8e-b6e5-9f526cc7bd97","title":"Засунуть сменку в рюкзак","content":{"items":[{"id":"87470bc3-404d-4fd6-aa5b-f93b766bf0be","type":"text","text":"Я решил засунуть сменку в рюкзак. ","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"d1f6b020-497c-4a7d-997d-f6ce2358e058","type":"text","text":"Только сейчас я вспомнил, что первым уроком алгебра. Довольно страшно заходить в этот кабинет когда ты опоздал. Лучше я прогуляюсь по школе","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"e2a16e0f-fd46-44d5-a559-817483a57fd3","type":"button","text":"Дальше","targetNodeId":"d1a57a97-599d-42a7-ac53-49da0438a90e","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-125.0,"y":600.0,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0,"color":4280492835},{"id":"6ddca9f8-283a-4d24-a159-d0b043bd5c22","chapterId":"caf88652-0509-4d8e-b6e5-9f526cc7bd97","title":"Дождаться звонка здесь","content":{"items":[{"id":"34972713-f0db-43b5-b431-0a36dff3fb27","type":"text","text":"Я решил дождаться звонка здесь.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"f256941b-f561-4bc9-98f4-0ec616443c9a","type":"text","text":"Я сел на скамейку и достал телефон. Залип в какую то пиксельную игру где мы прыгает по стенам с разными скинами и локациями.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"f2f9ffda-4f7d-4bec-80bf-ffa660671158","type":"wait_input","text":"Нажмите для продолжения","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"43d17d16-4072-46b7-88c3-99a64ac76b09","type":"audio","resourcePath":"res/audio/513d8f03-cd12-44a5-a600-ce6172205313.mp3","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"8188d27c-1c72-4e80-8cd2-90b4e399b63a","type":"text","text":"Прошло 20 минут и прозвенел звонок.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"ec5b2a96-8e5c-43f7-9aa7-678110dc8373","type":"text","text":"Чуть позже гардероб открыли, я быстро повесил сменку и вышел.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"137b06b8-9ff9-4d60-b859-94539528a548","type":"button","text":"Идти на литературу","targetNodeId":"744e68a9-4af6-4d7f-8790-7fd5e4a9d503","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":125.0,"y":600.0,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0,"color":4280492835},{"id":"d1a57a97-599d-42a7-ac53-49da0438a90e","chapterId":"caf88652-0509-4d8e-b6e5-9f526cc7bd97","title":"Дальше","content":{"items":[{"id":"6d82f6f1-5039-4db4-a67f-3a16a54fb2b8","type":"text","text":"Я прогуливаюсь по коридорам и вижу впереди Руми. Она выглядела как и всегда: Короткие коричневые волосы, карие глаза, джинсовка поверх футболки и джинсы. Она тоже опоздала?","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"a6236d88-34dd-43c1-ba0d-83bafac0a7cf","type":"button","text":"Поздороваться","targetNodeId":"66da3114-47fe-48df-a1d8-e16ac7f952a4","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-125.0,"y":800.0,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0,"color":4280492835},{"id":"744e68a9-4af6-4d7f-8790-7fd5e4a9d503","chapterId":"caf88652-0509-4d8e-b6e5-9f526cc7bd97","title":"Идти на литературу","content":{"items":[{"id":"7fd2d5b8-0fb8-4d1e-91f6-71ded265712c","type":"text","text":"Я зашел в класс и сел на свое место. Предпоследняя парта третьего ряда. На последней парте уже сидела Руми. Она выглядела как и всегда: Короткие коричневые волосы, карие глаза, джинсовка поверх футболки и джинсы. Ричард еще не подошёл. ","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"55f4985d-97dd-4c32-a748-8eef8be327de","type":"text","text":"Руми: Здорова, Кай, я уже думала ты не придёшь. Эй, слушай, мы с Ричардом хотели тебе сегодня рассказать. Недалеко от школы есть дорога ведущая к лесу, ты в курсе?","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"3fc0fbb8-7447-487f-89c5-29af08406962","type":"text","text":"Кай: Не поверишь, сколько лет учусь здесь, ни разу не видел. ","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"91341a40-c38d-4bee-92b2-8f7753f03215","type":"text","text":"Руми: (Не поняла это сейчас был сарказм?) В любом случае мы думали прогуляться там, ты с нами?","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"eef12acd-f692-4759-ac50-52d8b42b386a","type":"button","text":"Конечно","targetNodeId":"2756b8ab-18ab-4ca8-ba76-0e5b9acafcd6","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":125.0,"y":800.0,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0,"backgroundAudioId":"938e0e35-c715-452c-9570-96ff05789420.mp3","backgroundAssetId":"e3d07ec9-2a1b-4422-b0c7-2987e2601869.jpg"},{"id":"66da3114-47fe-48df-a1d8-e16ac7f952a4","chapterId":"caf88652-0509-4d8e-b6e5-9f526cc7bd97","title":"Поздороваться","content":{"items":[{"id":"9c1f79c3-f416-47f6-991a-f9e8384a90be","type":"text","text":"Кай: Привет!","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"73ab8edb-3e3a-4921-b79c-075e8a5aba78","type":"text","text":"Руми: Здорова, Кай, я так поняла ты тоже опоздал?","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"a7bbe6bf-ca80-490f-ad37-f0f9d3c6b718","type":"text","text":"Кай: Ага.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"a5dcaaaa-da4a-41dc-b505-a1f44a1e218f","type":"text","text":"Руми: Эй, слушай, мы с Ричардом хотели тебе сегодня рассказать. Недалеко от школы есть дорога ведущая к лесу, ты в курсе?","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"94aa7446-2fa3-4f41-a304-651a74e1e9a0","type":"text","text":"Кай: Не поверишь, сколько лет учусь здесь, ни разу не видел. ","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"b1b7edc1-4940-4a1d-a348-632d31618af1","type":"text","text":"Руми: (Не поняла это сейчас был сарказм?) В любом случае мы думали прогуляться там, ты с нами?","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"a19ac0e2-2630-4da5-92e2-c46687be4da5","type":"button","text":"Конечно","targetNodeId":"1a621723-6d4f-4f2b-a8f7-e6f2ec15215e","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-125.0,"y":1000.0,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"2756b8ab-18ab-4ca8-ba76-0e5b9acafcd6","chapterId":"caf88652-0509-4d8e-b6e5-9f526cc7bd97","title":"Конечно","content":{"items":[{"id":"ef398fed-431c-4150-9f3c-79fe50b21fa1","type":"text","text":"Руми: Отлично, сходим туда после школы!","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"1c4ea07a-df6e-40ec-897e-f297d9409d4d","type":"wait_input","text":"Нажмите для продолжения","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"ab89b26d-5a89-4534-bd93-ff2928e237e5","type":"audio","resourcePath":"res/audio/513d8f03-cd12-44a5-a600-ce6172205313.mp3","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"7e8c4317-b525-4a5a-a93d-a20f064a78ed","type":"text","text":"Прозвенел звонок и начался урок.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"f5e76155-ac38-42a9-9f3d-20eac48c875c","type":"button","text":"Дальше","targetNodeId":"e2ed294e-c455-476a-ab80-38d28bb0272d","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":131.18318465522105,"y":997.5267261379117,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0,"backgroundAudioId":"938e0e35-c715-452c-9570-96ff05789420.mp3","backgroundAssetId":"e3d07ec9-2a1b-4422-b0c7-2987e2601869.jpg"},{"id":"1a621723-6d4f-4f2b-a8f7-e6f2ec15215e","chapterId":"caf88652-0509-4d8e-b6e5-9f526cc7bd97","title":"Конечно","content":{"items":[{"id":"8a296365-ce00-421c-8a96-43e0982ab3c3","type":"text","text":"Руми: Отлично, сходим туда после уроков!","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"8406a7ac-768f-4d75-8214-f0d0144b3517","type":"wait_input","text":"Нажмите для продолжения","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"45d6117d-507c-42c5-a3c4-718965ee1834","type":"audio","resourcePath":"res/audio/513d8f03-cd12-44a5-a600-ce6172205313.mp3","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"bd709691-5c03-4831-912e-1ceb1d9925ce","type":"text","text":"Прозвенел звонок и я с Руми пошли на литературу.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"4d34a950-d2ad-4920-a52e-6fa14681fa01","type":"button","text":"Дальше","targetNodeId":"e2ed294e-c455-476a-ab80-38d28bb0272d","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-124.82462450582825,"y":1202.3377532568056,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"e2ed294e-c455-476a-ab80-38d28bb0272d","chapterId":"caf88652-0509-4d8e-b6e5-9f526cc7bd97","title":"Дальше","content":{"items":[{"id":"97fe22dc-5f54-4001-a226-5bfc2a1e280d","type":"text","text":"Посередине урока в класс заходит Ричард. Он тоже особо не изменился. Тёмные волосы, растрепанная причёска, карие(почти черные) глаза, темно серая толстовка, и широкие серые штаны. Его ругают за опоздание и он садится ко мне.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"321afeea-b166-4b5c-b11c-d09ff7fca723","type":"text","text":"Первым делом Ричард обратился к Руми.\nРичард: Ты сказала ему?","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"1150e8f6-a3af-451b-9bb8-efad6dfb315e","type":"text","text":"Руми: Да, он с нами!","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"b9c26d6d-3920-4c3b-bb6e-117d3d54a7e9","type":"text","text":"Ричард: Круто.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"8673defd-f3e7-4c8b-b095-547bcb304ea4","type":"button","text":"Поспать","targetNodeId":"faef3ee9-6d2d-4b52-a901-6744e7db9e25","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":129.6317107394226,"y":1201.1320324170745,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0,"backgroundAssetId":"e3d07ec9-2a1b-4422-b0c7-2987e2601869.jpg","backgroundAudioId":"938e0e35-c715-452c-9570-96ff05789420.mp3"},{"id":"faef3ee9-6d2d-4b52-a901-6744e7db9e25","chapterId":"caf88652-0509-4d8e-b6e5-9f526cc7bd97","title":"Поспать","content":{"items":[{"id":"171a31ec-f4d1-40a0-a3da-c90d1e28886b","type":"text","text":"Я как обычно спал практически на всех уроках. Только проклятая физра не позволила мне отдохнуть. Но этот учебный день наконец подошёл к концу. Я вышел из школы и Ричардом и Руми.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"be46804a-4854-4de9-b1dc-6e71d020611f","type":"text","text":"Руми: Ну что идем?\nКай: Идем!\nРичард одобрительно кивнул.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"42f1193b-05a1-4e52-bd4f-4a3c47d47ecc","type":"button","text":"Дальше","targetNodeId":"913edc3b-4ad0-4b98-88e2-1ebd3d41ef02","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":126.97097652319518,"y":1392.5350694651192,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0,"backgroundAssetId":"11d60557-c8c1-4916-9a19-83b70fe03abd.jpg"},{"id":"913edc3b-4ad0-4b98-88e2-1ebd3d41ef02","chapterId":"caf88652-0509-4d8e-b6e5-9f526cc7bd97","title":"Дальше","content":{"items":[{"id":"feb49780-a5df-4b34-afc2-338b94bdd577","type":"text","text":"Мы втроем шли по дороге. Осеннее солнце еще припекало, но уже по-осеннему — слабо и будто издалека. Листья под ногами шуршали так громко, что казалось, будто мы идем по чему-то живому.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"1e1c0674-e931-4002-870e-94c3712b559b","type":"text","text":"Кай: Люблю осень...","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"6cff97d7-d2ac-498f-ad4f-da4e0e5e83f4","type":"text","text":"Руми: Да... Красота, запах сырости...","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"2140617a-98db-4b16-a0e4-c621f20e979e","type":"text","text":"Ричард: Начало учебного года, постоянная усталость.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"ea81e87b-cbc1-4660-a81f-b26054cefda7","type":"text","text":"Руми: Ой, да завали а.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"6135e3d1-38f5-4aed-bcf1-ebaccbf7feae","type":"button","text":"Дальше","targetNodeId":"1abf25c0-ff9f-49f0-99f8-c027c23f7a70","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":115.98354284479436,"y":1658.3433103565437,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0,"backgroundAssetId":"11d60557-c8c1-4916-9a19-83b70fe03abd.jpg","backgroundAudioId":"374e32af-e9a9-43af-ad7a-044ebba12a3f.mp3"},{"id":"1abf25c0-ff9f-49f0-99f8-c027c23f7a70","chapterId":"bd73920b-bd52-4074-983d-f0be5472470a","title":"Лес","content":{"items":[{"id":"d7cb9614-dc43-4ee1-bc71-6bbd2b52778e","type":"text","text":"Лес встречает сыростью и тишиной. Воздух плотный, пропитанный запахом прелой листвы, мокрой коры и отсыревшей земли. Где-то в глубине едва уловимо пахнет грибами.\n\nНоги утопают в ковре из листьев — багряных, золотых, охряных. Они глушат шаги, лишь изредка выдавая влажный хруст. Капли с веток срываются на воротник холодными прикосновениями.\n\nТуман стелется между стволами, размывая очертания. Деревья, голые и мокрые, чернеют углём на фоне серого, низкого неба. Лишь кое-где на рябине ещё держатся гроздья, яркие, но бесполезные в этой промозглой мгле.\n\nГде-то далеко каркает ворона, и этот резкий звук тонет в вязкой тишине, не встречая отклика. По коже бегут мурашки от пронизывающей, застойной влажности, от которой не спасает даже плотная одежда. Всё вокруг замерло в ожидании первых заморозков.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"121abae6-27aa-49e6-9050-d6a994f08c83","type":"text","text":"Внезапно мы услышали чьи то голоса. Казалось бы, неудивительно, мы ведь не зашли в глубь леса... Но эти голоса доносились именно оттуда.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"76371442-5025-40b9-865f-4d0df7d2274b","type":"text","text":"Руми: Слышите?","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"a12c18b8-57b2-4d56-a392-7cadb4a812b7","type":"text","text":"Ричард: Да... Один голос до боли знаком...","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"3eb7d506-20ac-4e2c-a4d4-a92c3ee486b1","type":"text","text":"Кай: Сара?","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"1e78856c-47ac-4836-adb7-6730fc2841d5","type":"button","text":"Пойти на голоса","targetNodeId":"4b5f89b7-5ae4-4407-81e8-78d8e510ba1e","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":190.22222222222223,"y":419.2,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"4b5f89b7-5ae4-4407-81e8-78d8e510ba1e","chapterId":"bd73920b-bd52-4074-983d-f0be5472470a","title":"Пойти на голоса","content":{"items":[{"id":"ed226939-68da-4518-876b-bfb747464c12","type":"text","text":"Мы пошли на голоса и увидели Сару(нашу однокласницу). Она была в фиолетовой толстовке и тёмных штанах. Длинные черные волосы и черные глаза. Она сидела на полу, рядом с ней 3 \"ровных пацанчика\". Они смеются над ней и от их противного смеха мне хотелось закрыть уши.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"7f18bce6-3ee9-45c4-becb-0e0bdadce862","type":"wait_input","text":"Проваливайте отсюда, уроды!","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"2a44d8bd-056e-45d7-a136-c4b4188f38b4","type":"text","text":"?1: Пфф, смотрите, защитники пришли.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"92df2e1b-9125-4d93-8a16-e294b040e301","type":"text","text":"Ричард саркастично закатил глаза.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"7512deb3-7faa-4c2d-89cf-bfcdeb990efb","type":"text","text":"Ричард: О нет... Ровные пацанчики.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"df69ea78-1e2b-4749-abcc-b95f2425e68b","type":"text","text":"Руми выставила палец вперед в знак неуважения.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"ca70d63e-3075-4cae-8cdd-a6b5b0d04ed3","type":"text","text":"Руми: Да у них пульс ровный!","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"c7dfd948-66ae-4e22-a215-b6acf00230ca","type":"text","text":"?2: Че ты там вякнула, че думаешь самая умная?","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"99fa89f1-2a4c-41c8-acf0-8e632ccb3fa3","type":"text","text":"Руми: Ну точно поумнее твоей жирной мамашки!","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"60b38d2b-6d27-42bb-a2b5-438333519a7b","type":"text","text":"?3: Может вам зубы выбить?","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"03c29a38-ffca-4319-88d8-29530d90ba2f","type":"text","text":"Я взял камень, что был потяжелее и кинул в одного из них. Попал прямо в лицо!","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"ba897811-0153-4db9-bf3b-ae303aeb7ef7","type":"text","text":"Ричард: Да ты меткий.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"f8791783-5b63-4cc7-8ebb-b7cdb5ff5e4a","type":"text","text":"Все трое пошли на нас.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"d34426ce-2b41-400f-a1fc-a401a391dc27","type":"button","text":"Дальше","targetNodeId":"bfbc7dbb-0d59-4ab2-8738-47a23acb20bb","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":192.1777777777778,"y":649.0666666666667,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0,"backgroundAudioId":"c41fc10b-2b3e-448a-9955-86d176f571c6.mp3"},{"id":"bfbc7dbb-0d59-4ab2-8738-47a23acb20bb","chapterId":"bd73920b-bd52-4074-983d-f0be5472470a","title":"Дальше","content":{"items":[{"id":"d4e48721-9f78-4c3c-ba03-48e9482bb6f9","type":"text","text":"Один из них замахнулся на меня с кулаком.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"b36d5ef2-d1ef-4cd9-a0a0-c26df9ec3270","type":"wait_input","text":"Уворот","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"3233d301-c786-44a6-af4b-cfc4fe7d58cb","type":"wait_input","text":"Уворот","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"a89919b1-f036-4d2e-ad0e-6eb021f54098","type":"wait_input","text":"Уворот","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"df0c1456-b182-44e9-97e9-80c33916356c","type":"wait_input","text":"Уворот","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"30a46765-b9c9-4c00-9f89-83a757771470","type":"wait_input","text":"Уворот","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"e757defe-ff84-4394-8e88-5da9b766c726","type":"wait_input","text":"Уворот","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"59d4d642-4fca-40c5-9078-27fea1410246","type":"wait_input","text":"Уворот","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"51671826-a48f-405b-99a5-46b84505e073","type":"wait_input","text":"Уворот","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"f0573ec4-14b8-4a01-bb7f-d611d718065c","type":"wait_input","text":"Уворот","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"489778ca-c112-4558-ba7c-0ead11d9516b","type":"button","text":"Ударить","targetNodeId":"90af2cd3-e0fe-41ca-8a2a-7a894b86ad2e","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":170.26666666666668,"y":891.6888888888889,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0,"backgroundAudioId":"796a71a8-75df-4f2c-a0c9-e0a402e9fa1c.mp3","timerDuration":5.0,"defaultActionNodeId":"8bfc0231-c585-4d82-b9fc-51a63e0f777b"},{"id":"8bfc0231-c585-4d82-b9fc-51a63e0f777b","chapterId":"bd73920b-bd52-4074-983d-f0be5472470a","title":"Оу...","content":{"items":[{"id":"6cd20b4f-3a54-4c0e-8718-c52296859843","type":"text","text":"Все должно было быть не совсем так... Попробую снова!","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"20d53638-d89f-4d87-afc6-54f893f23a45","type":"button","text":"Заново","targetNodeId":"4b5f89b7-5ae4-4407-81e8-78d8e510ba1e","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":453.15555555555557,"y":852.4444444444439,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"90af2cd3-e0fe-41ca-8a2a-7a894b86ad2e","chapterId":"bd73920b-bd52-4074-983d-f0be5472470a","title":"Удар","content":{"items":[{"id":"1a724ee8-01a5-45e2-b7c0-5c32f6cf4bf1","type":"text","text":"Я ударил его в нос. Неуверен, что бил правильно, но точно сильно.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"e02af84e-e886-4fcf-b061-8ba7a3d34dbc","type":"text","text":"Руми почти сломала одному руку, Ричард просто стоял в стороне.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"9c89eb6e-03e8-40de-9d8b-5471d9ac61dd","type":"text","text":"Они ушли!","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"e8a6e339-0851-4491-b7b7-86f4d518b9d4","type":"button","text":"Дальше","targetNodeId":"c74cf901-c95d-40c1-9d11-1d58781be0d1","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":167.73333333333335,"y":1097.1555555555556,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0,"backgroundAudioId":"796a71a8-75df-4f2c-a0c9-e0a402e9fa1c.mp3"},{"id":"c74cf901-c95d-40c1-9d11-1d58781be0d1","chapterId":"bd73920b-bd52-4074-983d-f0be5472470a","title":"Сара","content":{"items":[{"id":"60741722-5705-4869-98f5-a67f77687936","type":"text","text":"Руми протянула Саре руку.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"d317d90d-9aa4-4035-8986-53366e756ceb","type":"text","text":"Кай: Ты как?","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"e759a39f-0dc3-40f8-9cea-95b8088908c2","type":"text","text":"Сара: Нормально.. Спасибо.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"d7657688-f1e7-4c26-81af-33ada0359eb1","type":"text","text":"Ричард: А что ты здесь делала?","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"6420f7d4-b97f-4af3-ade8-ef9155bcea26","type":"text","text":"Сара: Хотела сократить путь до дома и пойти напрямую через лес.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"8cbcbe14-a042-4662-ad65-2bcbe6905023","type":"text","text":"Руми: Давай с нами гулять!","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"83a6af49-d475-4d26-a1f9-9d37a01a3741","type":"text","text":"Сара: ... Почему бы и нет?.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"bd6f6b9c-9475-48ed-87e0-d3bf351683d2","type":"wait_input","text":"Эй, а что это там?","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"82a4e1e4-538a-48aa-b243-bd667633dc49","type":"text","text":"Я обратил внимание на домик посреди леса.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"5e6b784a-723b-44f1-b32b-be420834ccb8","type":"text","text":"Руми: Пойдёмте посмотрим.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"ba9de5cc-3568-4462-8299-13b7a5a42c75","type":"button","text":"Дальше","targetNodeId":"c68351b9-b4ea-4055-a9c3-30d05165f8d3","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":166.8392510011849,"y":1323.8897871342726,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"c68351b9-b4ea-4055-a9c3-30d05165f8d3","chapterId":"bd73920b-bd52-4074-983d-f0be5472470a","title":"Дальше","content":{"items":[{"id":"6f670b0b-bc14-4ab2-beb1-12084f446a92","type":"image","resourcePath":"res/images/38ee88df-e3e7-4efb-bf80-34f5442a287a.jpg","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"0e45d9a0-08dd-4406-bd55-04c63bbee9e9","type":"text","text":"Ричард: Заброшка посреди леса. Выглядит так, будто мы должны туда зайти.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"c746ebb2-7547-49de-9301-b6c8d86698e5","type":"text","text":"Сара: А может не стоит?","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"a59fc373-fe24-4e58-95e8-25f9592ac54b","type":"text","text":"Кай: Да мы и не на таких заброшках бывали.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"86fc7bac-9634-4ac6-9400-b161f879b8f9","type":"button","text":"Зайти","targetNodeId":"db79c997-3595-494d-a3db-717f6f20fd35","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":144.99431799644915,"y":1527.1284264692845,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0,"backgroundAudioId":"e3c8a64e-574d-47b5-9019-43fa1aeb661b.mp3"},{"id":"db79c997-3595-494d-a3db-717f6f20fd35","chapterId":"bd73920b-bd52-4074-983d-f0be5472470a","title":"Зайти","content":{"items":[{"id":"7ea2d178-277b-4c5f-b96a-a9547cb08b3d","type":"text","text":"Заброшенный снаружи дом выглядел внутри довольно уютно.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"5ca5af25-7047-41f4-a10a-e4269f9b5ca1","type":"text","text":"Ричард: Странно...","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"388cdda1-a36c-460e-bcef-6256ebc93a48","type":"text","text":"Сара: Может быть он стал заброшенным совсем недавно?...","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"4fb8c22b-c265-4755-954b-88dc6140d483","type":"text","text":"Пока все рассуждали о доме я нашел нечто, что заинтересовало меня больше.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"527ea9dc-0034-4435-beab-74fce9432f7c","type":"wait_input","text":"Взять","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"4dd3c0b7-8d74-4258-9e76-dc81ab3b03a8","type":"row","children":[{"id":"f1b0d808-6328-4add-8d0d-b7f04015c8b2","type":"image","resourcePath":"res/images/e579122f-2dfd-4850-a260-5103e76f0f0d.png","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"439a7b82-2559-4379-a8e0-d17bfc9e1dcc","type":"text","text":"Топор","flex":2,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}],"flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"9f1cd597-187e-4058-b9ee-58895ec0b8f1","type":"text","text":"Кай: Эй, зацените!","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"9317d591-a49b-4f50-b447-54e36b9c8983","type":"text","text":"Руми: Ого....","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"5c59e7ce-6762-4d94-968a-4eb0d9bd52d1","type":"text","text":"Кай: Возьму его домой!","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"6506fc9a-1021-4e16-9874-f6165b8b7c6d","type":"text","text":"Сара: Ты ведь шутишь?","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"e12ce3ed-57aa-4537-9189-6085fa64e8cb","type":"text","text":"Ричард: Поверь, он не шутит.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"f4c965da-fd90-4521-9f90-a5d8a72bb662","type":"text","text":"Руми: Надо запомнить это место... Будем собираться здесь иногда.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"38fea1cc-feaa-448c-aa99-393a010bdb9e","type":"text","text":"Сара: На заброшке?!","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"e05ff65a-2984-4230-b106-0ad0fad22818","type":"text","text":"Кай: Ну да, мы так всегда делаем. Просто предыдущий наш многоэтажный заброшенный дом попал под охрану.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"04313f63-fb38-436d-a2cd-fdadb794c066","type":"text","text":"Сара: И вы больше не могли туда попасть?","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"4fadf0f0-233f-470e-ba93-ab777e79f474","type":"text","text":"Кай: Не, мы перестали туда ходить после того как нас спалили, когда мы 10-ый раз прибирались туда.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"a7b4d697-3096-4d78-9e00-4feeb97cface","type":"text","text":"Руми: Ладно, пойдёмте по домам.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"e84fcac1-9cac-48d5-b485-4af4a87f74b8","type":"wait_input","text":"Выйти из дома","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"35c72efe-4eca-4778-af1a-e54cbc8c63be","type":"text","text":"Я дёрнул за ручку... Заперто?","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"679e32ce-2549-4532-a06d-6db7ad2e6ccf","type":"text","text":"Руми: Вылезем через окно?","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"c6e62699-98ef-4146-b79d-84a379217e52","type":"text","text":"Ричард: Не погоди... как деревянная [color=#FFDB00]почти сломанная[/color] дверь может быть заперта?","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"48a8037f-914b-4a1c-a13a-ae4e2f32ad6e","type":"text","text":"_______","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"e3542103-f894-4bdd-86f5-7d97095af1b1","type":"text","text":"Прочность двери: {Дверь}","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"8840e5e5-5ece-43b5-ab0f-a2fa905c3a0e","type":"row","children":[{"id":"799aa07b-1064-472e-bed3-e19c39b43679","type":"image","resourcePath":"res/images/e579122f-2dfd-4850-a260-5103e76f0f0d.png","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"c86e7c62-74ce-4bfb-89f9-bbc6e7f437fb","type":"button","text":"Топор","scriptTriggers":{"onPress":"scripts/550f969c-040d-4a03-806b-421e56df4856.json"},"flex":2,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}],"flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":147.29204847826261,"y":1745.1022115614774,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0,"backgroundAudioId":"e3c8a64e-574d-47b5-9019-43fa1aeb661b.mp3","backgroundAssetId":"bfe61f9e-33a1-4f45-8daa-f65a8320dc79.jpg"},{"id":"da5174f5-0ed3-418f-ac19-56eae74f6367","chapterId":"bd73920b-bd52-4074-983d-f0be5472470a","title":"Выход","content":{"items":[{"id":"c93044a2-af71-42f5-84d6-8b1b1fbe8eeb","type":"text","text":"Руми: М-да... Ну спасибо, Кай, теперь наша заброшка без двери. А ведь могли просто выйти через окно.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"f05220d4-68ab-4329-9050-e3932dca99cb","type":"text","text":"Кай: Сорян, мне просто хотелось сломать что нибудь топором.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"b0593499-13a6-4e5c-b710-2416f3f28b48","type":"text","text":"Сара: Так что, по домам?","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"49e4ab5e-3abf-49f5-93e4-639cfb48f07e","type":"text","text":"Ричард: Ага.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"44e80979-ecad-42e5-9238-0a8897b8e25d","type":"button","text":"Дальше","targetNodeId":"f15cb3ad-3bd5-4532-a627-7cdca6ef757c","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":154.36652182677682,"y":1948.3408508964894,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0,"backgroundAssetId":"38ee88df-e3e7-4efb-bf80-34f5442a287a.jpg"},{"id":"f15cb3ad-3bd5-4532-a627-7cdca6ef757c","chapterId":"bd73920b-bd52-4074-983d-f0be5472470a","title":"Закат","content":{"items":[{"id":"e8cd59d6-997a-4494-8525-3fb04196fa5c","type":"text","text":"Сара: Да уж... Долго же мы гуляли.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"4059e686-9c86-441d-a783-b2e0a114476b","type":"text","text":"Руми: Ага, надо будет повторить!","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"73a4bb2a-dcfd-410a-98ae-ae000cc28ac0","type":"button","text":"Дальше","targetNodeId":"9bdd3317-2cc5-4d8b-b08b-62585b0c0277","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":136.14239783604603,"y":2225.2340423419296,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0,"backgroundAssetId":"f823d8eb-46a1-483c-ac9c-b9047bbf24f4.jpg"},{"id":"9bdd3317-2cc5-4d8b-b08b-62585b0c0277","chapterId":"8c148ebf-0109-4a22-828b-acc7685a6627","title":"Конец 1 главы","content":{"items":[{"id":"8a8df843-5b02-401a-b7d3-64d4dcdc59fd","type":"text","text":"Так и прошёл мой день. До завтра, дорогой дневник.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"8c24f43f-554e-4fa9-88b6-cb3ef6688c5f","type":"wait_input","text":"Нажмите для продолжения","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"8eb1cfaf-2cb5-40d3-a290-4c2795493c71","type":"text","text":"*Shedevro Bobr*: Эта глава вышла линейной, хотя изначально я планировал уже в ней сделать выходы на другие ветки. Постараюсь сделать это во второй главе. Эта история будет серьёзней чем кажется сейчас, поверьте. Если вам понравилось или вы просто хотите сказать что нибудь об этом квесте, я всегда люблю читать отзывы(буду признателен развёрнутому отзыву с честной оценкой и конструктивный критикой).","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"0a58b727-6d5a-4414-b811-2c5e4eb0c810","type":"button","text":"Меню","targetNodeId":"3e58c4f3-2424-4ca6-b095-cfd2610fe2e8","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":192.0,"y":416.0,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"3e58c4f3-2424-4ca6-b095-cfd2610fe2e8","chapterId":"05728932-8bf5-46cb-8d95-9af044bdbcd4","title":"Дневник","content":{"items":[{"id":"4876345f-41a8-48b5-9529-53b9354fb376","type":"image","resourcePath":"res/images/625850e3-31e9-4a9c-bc3b-daadb4bab77f.png","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"eae57191-f74d-4771-b4e4-f4d900b87f18","type":"text","text":"Музыка взята из игры \"Deltarune\"","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"997eca1d-95b5-4f86-9265-19a3ae9170dd","type":"text","text":"Предупреждение о тригерах:\nВ этом квесте поднимаются серьезные темы подростковых взаимоотношений, включая сцены буллинга и специфический черный юмор. Также в окружении вы найдете холодное оружие — оно является частью мира, но не используется для причинения вреда персонажам ЛЮДЯМ. Если вы остро реагируете на темы травли, пожалуйста, позаботьтесь о своем комфорте заранее.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"b1109ff1-e99d-4d79-a4a5-1c4df4bf40a5","type":"button","text":"Начать","targetNodeId":"d33261ae-e044-4deb-80cd-d35a94cca3e6","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":192.0,"y":416.0,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"d33261ae-e044-4deb-80cd-d35a94cca3e6","chapterId":"05728932-8bf5-46cb-8d95-9af044bdbcd4","title":"Имя","content":{"items":[{"id":"3665227c-cc81-444e-bf61-e1f82c3c166c","type":"text","text":"Дорогой дневник, моё имя Кай Эйр.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"822c99c1-67ac-43b4-b4dc-30510bd8bb48","type":"button","text":"Глава 1","targetNodeId":"1aeacca8-df99-4d1e-b22a-253661dcc4fb","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":196.62222222222223,"y":606.5777777777776,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0}],"groups":[],"comments":[]}